Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.18,0:33:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,now before Abraham
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.18,0:33:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I was
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.18,0:33:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.18,0:33:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,who was before Abraham
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.18,0:33:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,God
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.18,0:33:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.30,0:33:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.30,0:33:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,so what's the problem
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.62,0:33:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,well
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.62,0:33:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,before man
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.62,0:33:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,was God
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.62,0:33:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,divinity preceded the appearance of man
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.62,0:33:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,before Abraham
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.62,0:33:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,was
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.62,0:33:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Abraham
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.62,0:33:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.35,0:33:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,so what's the problem
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.35,0:33:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,well
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.35,0:33:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,before man
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.35,0:33:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,was God
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.35,0:33:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,was
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.35,0:33:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.35,0:33:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.35,0:33:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,there is a
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.35,0:33:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,a large movement
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.35,0:33:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,these days
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.35,0:33:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,of
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.35,0:33:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.35,0:33:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.35,0:33:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,it's
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.28,0:33:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,channeled
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.28,0:33:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,teachers
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.28,0:33:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that call themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.28,0:33:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Abraham
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.28,0:33:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,so I was
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.28,0:33:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,more asking
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.28,0:33:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,if there may be connection
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.28,0:33:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that actually
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.28,0:33:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,what this
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.28,0:33:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,no it's a different Abraham
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.28,0:33:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,they're talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.28,0:33:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,oh okay
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.28,0:33:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.28,0:33:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,they're talking about Abraham Hicks
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.28,0:33:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,different thing
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.28,0:33:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,there wasn't any Hicks
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.28,0:33:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,at the time of Jesus
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.28,0:34:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.20,0:34:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,she's confusing the name
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.33,0:34:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,you know the name
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.33,0:34:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.45,0:34:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,that's only nominalization
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.12,0:34:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't control what people ask me you know
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.82,0:34:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,well I'm not going to ask you anything
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.82,0:34:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,my weather
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.82,0:34:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,stormy weather field
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.82,0:34:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,likes to be in your weather field
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.47,0:34:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.47,0:34:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you bet
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.98,0:34:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to discern the level of truth of a statement
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.98,0:34:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you know you calibrate the level of truth you see
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.98,0:34:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't need a personal opinion
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.25,0:34:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,you just calibrate
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.25,0:34:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,what's the level of that
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.25,0:34:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and what's the level of this
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.25,0:35:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and they may come out of different contexts
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.25,0:35:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,hello Dr. Hawkins
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.31,0:35:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,one thing is true in this context
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.31,0:35:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and the other thing is true in this context
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.31,0:35:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,but this is not true in this context
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.31,0:35:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,you understand
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.31,0:35:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.31,0:35:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,hello Dr. Hawkins
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.31,0:35:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,you answer all my questions through your work
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.31,0:35:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm very grateful
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.31,0:35:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and I thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.31,0:35:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,however there is somebody very dear to me
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.31,0:35:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,who wants to ask you
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.31,0:35:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,a question
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.31,0:35:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,who wants what
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.31,0:35:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,who wants to ask a question
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.31,0:35:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,somebody wants to ask you a question
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.31,0:35:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,which is my dear wife
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.31,0:35:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,oh oh
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.31,0:35:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,where is she
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.31,0:35:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,she's at home
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.31,0:35:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,oh oh
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.31,0:35:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and she keeps asking me
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.31,0:35:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,how come a man
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.31,0:35:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,is meditating 3-4 hours a day
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.31,0:35:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and he's always with his tapes
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.31,0:35:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,with his headphones on his ears
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.31,0:35:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,a real man wouldn't do that
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.31,0:35:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and the only answer I can tell her
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.31,0:35:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,is that it's an attraction
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.31,0:35:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.31,0:35:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,it just happens
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.31,0:35:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and then she says
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.70,0:35:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,well day by day you're getting crazier and crazier
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.70,0:36:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you're getting as that old crazy guy on TV
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.32,0:36:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that you're watching at
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.32,0:36:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and I said God willing
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.32,0:36:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,so you turn me on to this
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.02,0:36:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,can you please turn her off
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.02,0:36:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,you have a divergence of alignment
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.20,0:36:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and many relationships end because of it
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.22,0:36:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,one gets God struck
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.67,0:36:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and the other doesn't
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.67,0:36:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and very often the one who doesn't is jealous
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.90,0:36:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and hates the one who's God struck
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.90,0:36:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,because they're not God struck
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.90,0:36:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and so they do end in divorce yes
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.38,0:36:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to choose between God and her
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.24,0:36:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's her decision isn't it
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.93,0:36:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,she's the one making the decision
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.93,0:36:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.93,0:37:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,she's the one that's turning away from God
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.34,0:37:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and you turn towards God
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.66,0:37:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,yes that can cause quite a divergence
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.66,0:37:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,so now I can go home in peace
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.56,0:37:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,you can go home and be
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.56,0:37:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,in peace
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.56,0:37:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,in peace I said
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.56,0:37:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,oh peace yeah yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.56,0:37:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,you answered the question thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.13,0:37:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,you pray for her
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.13,0:37:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,okay
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.13,0:37:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,well I committed that I will serve her as I would serve God
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.13,0:37:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,so let's see what that brings
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.13,0:37:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah okay
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.13,0:37:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.13,0:37:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you doctor
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.13,0:37:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.82,0:37:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,just pray secretly
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.82,0:37:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,don't let her know you're praying
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.82,0:37:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,while you're eating your toast in the morning
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.82,0:37:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and look at you you flip the page
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.82,0:37:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and see you're surreptitiously praying
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.82,0:37:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,how you doing doc
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.82,0:37:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,could you talk further about
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.82,0:37:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the identification with
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.82,0:38:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the light of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.02,0:38:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,about what
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.02,0:38:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,identification with the light of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.02,0:38:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,could you talk a little bit about that
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.78,0:38:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,it's by letting go what you are not
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.00,0:38:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that it's revealed to you
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.86,0:38:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that that which is the source of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.86,0:38:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and that which you are
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.27,0:38:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,are simultaneous
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.68,0:38:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,it isn't affirming what you are
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.68,0:38:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,because that's probably just a thought
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.09,0:38:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,instead you just constantly surrender
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.09,0:38:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,what you are not
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.09,0:38:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and where does awareness
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.27,0:38:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,does awareness come out of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.27,0:38:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the light is consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.88,0:38:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and awareness is like a quality of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.88,0:38:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.88,0:38:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,so the light of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.88,0:38:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,which is universe
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.04,0:38:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,is universal
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.55,0:38:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,out of the light of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.55,0:39:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,when it strikes matter arises life
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.55,0:39:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,see
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.42,0:39:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,because it is the source of life
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.42,0:39:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.42,0:39:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes protoplasmic life
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.42,0:39:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,when it encounters organic material
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.42,0:39:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,organic
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.64,0:39:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,not inorganic
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.64,0:39:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,but organic
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.64,0:39:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.47,0:39:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,so you let go of what you are not
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.47,0:39:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not necessary to affirm what you are
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.86,0:39:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,because what you are becomes
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.86,0:39:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,it's like surrendering
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.89,0:39:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,it just kind of reveals itself
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.89,0:39:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,it reveals itself
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.89,0:39:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and if one were to live in that silent space
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.27,0:39:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,all the time
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.27,0:39:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,what would happen to the ego and the experiencer
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.46,0:39:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,they disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.46,0:39:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.06,0:39:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.07,0:39:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,hello Dr. Hawkins
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.07,0:39:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.07,0:39:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,my question is
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.07,0:40:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,for someone who is looking to move eventually into the 400s
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.07,0:40:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and eventually transcend the 400s
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.07,0:40:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,would you recommend higher education or college
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.07,0:40:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,or is that necessary
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.07,0:40:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.10,0:40:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I think education helps
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.10,0:40:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,it just sharpens certain faculties
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.25,0:40:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,however it's not necessary
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.25,0:40:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not necessary
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.08,0:40:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,anything that lifts your level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.35,0:40:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,education, dedication, selfless service
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.80,0:40:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,any one of them will do it
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.80,0:40:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the Jesus prayer
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.86,0:40:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to merely say the Jesus prayer from within all the time
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.92,0:40:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't need to go to college to do that
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.37,0:40:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,see
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.37,0:40:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,so
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.50,0:40:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,it depends on what
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.50,0:40:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,how you picture your future life
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.50,0:40:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,if it's devoted to teaching
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.50,0:40:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,then the education would be beneficial
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.04,0:41:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,if instead you tend to become
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.46,0:41:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,more a spiritual initiate
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.97,0:41:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,then it's not necessary
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.97,0:41:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,you know some orders are
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.30,0:41:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,educative orders
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.34,0:41:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and then there are orders that are not educative
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.34,0:41:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,they are more of service
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.17,0:41:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,so you serve God by gardening
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.17,0:41:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and you also serve God by translating
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.20,0:41:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,doing the book of Kells
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.20,0:41:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,did you ever look up the book of Kells
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.58,0:41:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,K-E-L-L-S
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.12,0:41:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,you know
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.54,0:41:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,so you see the monks
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.54,0:41:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,spent lifetimes
