Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.16,0:56:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and I am not
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.16,0:57:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and one of the things which I noticed
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.16,0:57:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,was that
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.16,0:57:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.16,0:57:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the herbivorous animals
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.16,0:57:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,they are
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.16,0:57:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,more benign
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.16,0:57:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,or they are higher in scale
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.16,0:57:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,yes yes
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.16,0:57:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and I think we kind of have this discussion
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.16,0:57:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and I was wondering
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.16,0:57:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,if let's say humanity decided to be vegetarian
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.16,0:57:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,would it raise the level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.16,0:57:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,or
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.16,0:57:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,it doesn't matter
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.16,0:57:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,if everyone was vegetarian
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.16,0:57:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,would it raise the level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.16,0:57:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,no
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.16,0:57:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,vegetarianism calibrates at 210
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.32,0:57:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,which is not you know
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.32,0:57:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,going to knock over the globe
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.38,0:57:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,okay
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.38,0:57:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.38,0:57:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,all right
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.38,0:57:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.38,0:57:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.38,0:57:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,you just asserted being spiritual and a vegetarian
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.38,0:57:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,oh
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.66,0:57:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot of people say if you're not a vegetarian they'll kill you
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.79,0:57:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,environmentalism
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.79,0:57:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.82,0:57:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to express a profound gratefulness that I feel everywhere in this room for you
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.82,0:58:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.11,0:58:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,it's for the group
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.11,0:58:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.11,0:58:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a group
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.11,0:58:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I just feel it everywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.11,0:58:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,so I don't want to mention myself in that
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.11,0:58:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a pretty burning question for my whole life
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.11,0:58:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and it comes from other lifetimes
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.11,0:58:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and this one as well
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.11,0:58:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,is there a time
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.59,0:58:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,because I know on your map of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.59,0:58:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,that suicide rates at a negative 50
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.59,0:58:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,is there a time in a person's life
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.75,0:58:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,at the end of their life
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.75,0:58:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,when they're suffering
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.75,0:58:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's no
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.75,0:58:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,you know
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.75,0:58:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,dying
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.75,0:58:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,they're basically dying
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.75,0:58:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,is it
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.75,0:58:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,karmic
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.75,0:58:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,are there karmic repercussions for taking your own life
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.75,0:58:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,or assisting somebody in taking their life at that point
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.75,0:58:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,well you're asking about
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.64,0:58:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,you know
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.64,0:58:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,what does suicide calibrate at
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.64,0:58:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,depends on who's committing suicide
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.64,0:58:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and for what reason
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.64,0:58:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and in what context
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.64,0:59:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not necessary to commit suicide
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.41,0:59:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,if you want to die
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.43,0:59:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,just allow yourself to die
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.43,0:59:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,what's the problem
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.43,0:59:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,but not everybody knows
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.10,0:59:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,if someone wants to die
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.10,0:59:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,they can go in there
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.10,0:59:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,they can go in the garage
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.10,0:59:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and close the door
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.10,0:59:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and turn the engine on
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.10,0:59:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't need a doctor
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.10,0:59:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,to give any injection
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.90,0:59:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you know what I'm saying
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.90,0:59:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,so that's not a karmic
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.90,0:59:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no negative
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.90,0:59:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,that's trying to heap the responsibility
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.90,0:59:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,on the doctor and society
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.90,0:59:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,if you decide to leave the world
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.90,0:59:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,that's pretty easy to do isn't it
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.10,0:59:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.10,0:59:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,that doesn't have bad karmic repercussions
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.10,0:59:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't ask about that
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.10,0:59:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think we can ask
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.10,0:59:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,because it depends on who
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.10,0:59:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and in what context
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.10,0:59:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and what they think death is
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.10,0:59:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,right
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.35,0:59:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,so there are levels of death
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.35,0:59:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,so the motivation could be fear
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.35,0:59:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,of pain
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.35,0:59:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,fear
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.35,0:59:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.35,0:59:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,it could be cowardice
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.67,0:59:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.67,0:59:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,if you want to die
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.70,0:59:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,that's very very simple
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.70,0:59:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you how to do it for nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.15,0:59:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,stop eating
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.15,1:00:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,stop drinking fluid
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.15,1:00:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and lay on the floor
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.15,1:00:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have to hire a doctor
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.72,1:00:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,to come in and give you an injection
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.72,1:00:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,doctor death or somebody
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.72,1:00:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,you know
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.23,1:00:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'm hearing
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.12,1:00:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,to die
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.12,1:00:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,all you have to do is do nothing
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.38,1:00:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and you will automatically die
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.38,1:00:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.60,1:00:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you lay on the ground
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.76,1:00:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and you
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.76,1:00:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and the sun comes up
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.76,1:00:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and the sun comes down
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.76,1:00:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you become dehydrated
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.76,1:00:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you lapse into coma
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.76,1:00:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and you leave
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.76,1:00:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,what's the problem
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.76,1:00:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have to hire a video crew you know
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.47,1:00:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and make a big drama out of it
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.07,1:00:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,it's very simple to die
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.49,1:00:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,you let go wanting to live
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.52,1:00:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and you let go wanting to live
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.19,1:00:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the desire to live slips away
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.19,1:00:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and the breathing slows down and down
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.19,1:00:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and you can be very very close to death
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.06,1:00:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and still come back
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.06,1:00:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,because at the last moment you realize
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.14,1:00:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,it's still up to you
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.14,1:01:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you get the karmic implications
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.14,1:01:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and the meaning of this
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.14,1:01:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and you then may change your mind
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.14,1:01:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,it is you know
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.48,1:01:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,on one hand
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.48,1:01:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the reason we calibrate low
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.06,1:01:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,is because it's like negating divine mercy
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.06,1:01:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you see
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.06,1:01:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,as you're turning your life to God
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.05,1:01:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,you're turning it over to the divine mercy
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.05,1:01:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,in the death process
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.05,1:01:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,is then bearable
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.21,1:01:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,can even be ecstatic
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.21,1:01:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,out of God's grace is given the strength
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.15,1:01:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,to bear death
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.28,1:01:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,so constantly surrendered to God's grace in the matter
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.34,1:01:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,is what summons it forth
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.91,1:02:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to calibrate suicide because
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.14,1:02:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,people will go into a negative space of all of it
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.75,1:02:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,sometimes it can be an act of bravery and courage
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.24,1:02:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,other times it can be courage
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.24,1:02:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,it can be cowardice
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.24,1:02:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,so you don't know which is which
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.24,1:02:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,so you can't generalize it
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.24,1:02:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,it depends on who's doing it
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.24,1:02:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,or what motive
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.24,1:02:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.16,1:02:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,hello
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.80,1:02:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a way of committing suicide which is passive
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.28,1:02:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,in which you don't
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.28,1:02:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,you just don't resist death
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.28,1:02:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.53,1:02:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and then death takes over
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.53,1:02:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.53,1:02:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I have experienced chronic fatigue
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.53,1:02:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,for over six years
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.53,1:02:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,what
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.53,1:02:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,chronic fatigue
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.53,1:02:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.53,1:02:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'd just like to know what caused this
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.53,1:02:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and how to get over it
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.53,1:02:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I've
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.53,1:02:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,you're talking about a medical diagnosis
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.53,1:02:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been to about 15 doctors
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.53,1:02:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,it's been going on for a long time
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.53,1:02:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and I've tried different healing modalities
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.53,1:02:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,oh chronic fatigue syndrome
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.53,1:02:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,yes sir yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.53,1:02:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,CFS
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.53,1:03:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,well yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.53,1:03:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,okay
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.53,1:03:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,okay
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.53,1:03:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,there are many theories about it
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.53,1:03:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,chronic fatigue syndrome
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.53,1:03:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's also many
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.53,1:03:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,a whole set of modalities of treatment
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.53,1:03:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and I treated many in my lifetime
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.53,1:03:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,each one seemed to me to be different
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.72,1:03:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,there was no like
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.72,1:03:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,a cause of it
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.72,1:03:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,so I used to use a whole
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.10,1:03:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,bunch of things
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.26,1:03:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,nutritional
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.26,1:03:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.26,1:03:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,acupuncture
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.26,1:03:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,a whole variety of things
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.26,1:03:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.61,1:03:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget what the last
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.64,1:03:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,most powerful things I found were for
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.64,1:03:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I've sort of forgotten now
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.64,1:03:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,it's been some years since I've been in practice
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.74,1:03:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,antidepressants
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.74,1:03:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Prozac
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.74,1:03:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,various things
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.96,1:03:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you've probably been through all them yes
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.96,1:03:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,yes sir yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.96,1:03:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.96,1:03:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,all right
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.96,1:03:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,so then it could also be
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.96,1:03:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,some kind of a karmic propensity
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.96,1:03:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,could be a karmic propensity
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.41,1:03:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,chronic fatigue syndrome
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.41,1:04:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I've sort of forgotten all the different modalities
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.82,1:04:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to use
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.82,1:04:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,but there was about a dozen
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.82,1:04:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and about 90% of the time
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.95,1:04:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,one of them would work
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.95,1:04:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,you know one or the other would work
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.95,1:04:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,okay
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.95,1:04:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,okay
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.29,1:04:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,so nothing specific to my case
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.29,1:04:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,that you can pick up on that
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.29,1:04:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.29,1:04:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a causal link
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.29,1:04:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to run through a gamut
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.29,1:04:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,okay
