Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.10,1:13:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,specifically
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.16,1:13:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Specifically, does meat-eating calibrate lower than vegetarianism?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.20,1:13:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Vegetarianism calibrates 210.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.98,1:13:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, it doesn't have any spiritual positive or negative.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.06,1:13:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It would have only to the degree that you're fulfilling
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.24,1:13:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,what you feel is a spiritual obligation.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.66,1:13:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And most people go through a period of vegetarianism, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.46,1:13:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.12,1:13:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of one's intention to not harm living things.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.02,1:13:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And you don't incur any karmic debt from that?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.94,1:13:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.78,1:13:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The Rig Veda, you have to read the Rig Veda,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.18,1:13:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and you will understand what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.13,1:13:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Rig Veda.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.53,1:13:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Calories at 900.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.33,1:13:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.64,1:13:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Each thing earns its own transcendence
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.71,1:13:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,by serving that which is below it.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.15,1:13:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,By allowing myself to be eaten by humankind,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.65,1:14:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,the cattle earns its right to evolve
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.87,1:14:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,eventually to humanness.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.59,1:14:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,By my sacrifice to thee, O Lord of my life,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.27,1:14:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,to that which is higher,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.81,1:14:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,do I earn the karmic right to become higher?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.05,1:14:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Calvary's 900.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.69,1:14:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The Rig Veda recontextualizes the whole question.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.01,1:14:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I once saw it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.16,1:14:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw a bird that was caught by a hawk,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.36,1:14:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and I saw that the bird, I saw its spirit.
