Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.34,1:14:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.36,1:14:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.38,1:14:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.40,1:14:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.42,1:14:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.44,1:14:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I give myself to thee, O Lord, is what it was actually saying.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.61,1:14:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually saw it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.30,1:14:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the hawk again will surrender that which I am to thee, O Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.60,1:14:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And each one goes higher and higher.
