Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.79,1:15:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.92,1:15:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.92,1:15:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have his promotion, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.92,1:15:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The Native American manner of holding, the sacredness of the spirit of the animal, is
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.95,1:15:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,another way of acknowledging the divinity of the essence of life in all that lives,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.68,1:15:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and giving thanks to Almighty God for the life of the animal.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.04,1:15:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So the American Indian, you know, blesses the sacrifice of the animal, and thereby, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.88,1:15:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and thereby, affirms the divinity of all of life, you know, the sacredness of the great spirit.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.45,1:15:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Native American acknowledges the great spirit as a source of life.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.43,1:15:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So, God bless the two of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.67,1:15:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.45,1:16:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you in love, in love, and alignment in love.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.28,1:16:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.72,1:16:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And in love.
