Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.94,1:16:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.44,1:16:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going through a stack two weeks ago, and didn't get to sign the card, so I got
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.38,1:16:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you another one.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.68,1:16:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.26,1:16:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's a dollar for the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.50,1:16:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Kitty.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.55,1:16:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.61,1:17:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The stack has got to do with two things, but one of them is for the many years.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.78,1:17:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,various people connected to
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.10,1:17:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,a now deceased guru.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.64,1:17:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Connected to what?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.40,1:17:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,To a now deceased guru.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.40,1:17:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,To what?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.32,1:17:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A deceased guru.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.40,1:17:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Or deceased.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.32,1:17:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Deceased.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.82,1:17:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.10,1:17:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a very large organization
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.28,1:17:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and there are many people in there
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.38,1:17:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,who on many levels
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.09,1:17:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,are very wonderful people.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.41,1:17:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.19,1:17:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And I know that at one point
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.65,1:17:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,this guru calibrated fairly high
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.41,1:17:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,in the high 500s and then fell.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.07,1:17:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.29,1:17:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get that it was about sexuality,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.61,1:17:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,power, or those other things.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.55,1:17:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.01,1:17:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Would it be for opening up students
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.23,1:17:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,without properly preparing them?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.10,1:17:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be any defect.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.75,1:17:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean the guru fell?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.55,1:17:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The teacher fell?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.23,1:17:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.51,1:17:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that I don't have.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.31,1:18:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that you had calibrated him
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.07,1:18:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,at around 570
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.09,1:18:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and then he went down to the 100s.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.86,1:18:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's rather common, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.94,1:18:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't get that it was for the usual ones
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.14,1:18:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,or money, power, sex.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.54,1:18:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.56,1:18:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't get that from...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.42,1:18:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know what the reason is?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.98,1:18:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.54,1:18:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd have to be more involved
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.84,1:18:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and then it'll become apparent.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.02,1:18:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be more involved.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.42,1:18:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The person will become more secular,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.82,1:18:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,more interested in money, fame, power, glamour.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.74,1:18:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be any one of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.62,1:18:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Would opening...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.24,1:18:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Energetically opening a huge amount,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.90,1:18:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,a mass of people
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.90,1:18:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,without properly preparing them,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.38,1:18:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,would that also be one of...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.93,1:18:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Would that be a spiritual trap?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.73,1:18:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That'd be a control issue.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.41,1:18:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That'd be a control issue.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.37,1:18:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kind of a research question.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.37,1:18:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a research question,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.43,1:18:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,but what you're presenting as a possibility
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.91,1:18:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,is you're going to force people
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.31,1:19:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,to desire spiritual awareness
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.55,1:19:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,without their agreement, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.21,1:19:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.57,1:19:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm also thinking of myself
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.17,1:19:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,as a teacher and my responsibilities
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.97,1:19:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,to my students in terms of
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.65,1:19:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,is there a line?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.24,1:19:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess there is no real line
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.82,1:19:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,for any of this, is there?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.16,1:19:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, there is.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.40,1:19:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.94,1:19:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there's definitely a line.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.88,1:19:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So where do I find that line?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.00,1:19:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.96,1:19:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're mixing up a whole bunch of issues here.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.96,1:19:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.74,1:19:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're vague on your question,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.40,1:19:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's very difficult.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.66,1:19:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't control the consciousness level
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.60,1:19:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,of your students,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.46,1:19:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and you've got to let go
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.26,1:19:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,wanting to control that, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.84,1:19:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.28,1:19:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to force them
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.22,1:19:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to become enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.18,1:19:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.88,1:19:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.86,1:19:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's like the Shaktipat,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.64,1:19:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,which would be a forceful issue.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.06,1:19:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So what you do is
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.24,1:19:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you give them the information they need.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.78,1:19:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.36,1:19:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And as much encouragement as you can,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.24,1:19:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,but then the evolution is up to themselves,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.92,1:19:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,you see?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.46,1:19:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.08,1:19:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.52,1:20:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Or you teach them a certain technique
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.38,1:20:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,that will help them
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.14,1:20:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to achieve their spiritual goals, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.18,1:20:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.94,1:20:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so techniques are useful,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.42,1:20:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,but they're only a technique.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.22,1:20:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.18,1:20:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.80,1:20:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.12,1:20:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.30,1:20:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,like surrendering the,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.52,1:20:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,resisting the experiencing of time,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.32,1:20:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.56,1:20:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,it's only a technique, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.36,1:20:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.08,1:20:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.50,1:20:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.09,1:20:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.81,1:20:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Hustle.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.15,1:20:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.89,1:20:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.09,1:20:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This morning was exceptional
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.79,1:20:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,in its clarity
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.75,1:20:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and expansion
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.25,1:20:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,of our learning your work.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.46,1:20:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.56,1:20:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a group
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.12,1:20:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,that meets twice a month in Phoenix,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.83,1:20:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and what we've been doing
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.01,1:20:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,is showing a DVD
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.37,1:20:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,of a Sedona,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.51,1:20:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sedona presentation.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.93,1:20:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.73,1:20:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's on a weeknight evening,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.31,1:20:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,so we only have like an hour and a half to two hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.51,1:20:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Some are requesting that we pick a book
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.83,1:21:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and go through a paragraph at a time,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.27,1:21:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and others prefer that we watch a DVD
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.14,1:21:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and get a more like an overview.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.04,1:21:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it both ways.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.13,1:21:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes if you meet twice a week,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.03,1:21:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,one night you do a video,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.13,1:21:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and the next night you do a discussion,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.73,1:21:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,or discuss a book.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.73,1:21:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.95,1:21:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.95,1:21:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, both ways are used,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.95,1:21:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, like in AA,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.95,1:21:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,they will take a lesson for the day,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.95,1:21:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,12 steps,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.95,1:21:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,they'll do a step or a tradition,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.59,1:21:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,or because nowadays we have DVDs,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.68,1:21:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, they do a video.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.68,1:21:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.97,1:21:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.97,1:21:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.06,1:21:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.35,1:21:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.56,1:21:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.56,1:21:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.00,1:21:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Recently I've been doing a lot of releasing,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.00,1:22:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and now it just feels like
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.00,1:22:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't really feel any,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.10,1:22:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.10,1:22:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,emotions coming up,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.10,1:22:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,but only the,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.10,1:22:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.10,1:22:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the physical sensations in my stomach.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.10,1:22:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was wondering,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.45,1:22:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,is that normal,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.45,1:22:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,or am I actually supposed to be feeling something
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.45,1:22:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,when I'm surrendering?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.45,1:22:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's normal.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.45,1:22:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.40,1:22:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any,
